data.description: Motivated seller! This beautiful 2 story Sivage Thomas home is conveniently located in a cul-de-sac near schools, shopping and I-40 for easy commuting. It is a great family home with a landscaped and spacious backyard. The roof was recently replaced in October 2022. It also has a tankless water heater, and the garage door and opener were replaced in January of 2023.
